Class BooleanDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rapidminer.belt.column.Dictionary
      • com.rapidminer.belt.column.BooleanDictionary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Dictionary.Entry>
    public class BooleanDictionary
extends Dictionary
    A Dictionary that is boolean (see isBoolean(). It can have at most two values and knows a positive and/or negative index.
    Author:
    Gisa Meier
